import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom';
import App from "./App"
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';


ReactDOM.render(
    <React.StrictMode>
        <BudgetsContext>
            <App />
        </BudgetsContext>
    </React.StrictMode>,
    document.getElementById("root")
)
